  <brief_title>IS There a Correlation Between Sypmtoms of Gastroparesis and the Duration of Video Caspule Retention in the Stomach</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open Prospective Single Center Study for the Determination of Correlation Between Video Capsule Period of Retention in the Stomach and Symptoms of Gastroparesis</official_title>
